definitions.definition: One of a sovereign people indigenous to what is now Maritime Canada and the northeastern United States , particularly Maine .

main_definition: One of a sovereign people indigenous to what is now Maritime Canada and the northeastern United States , particularly Maine .

definitions.definition: An extinct Abenaki ( Algonquian ) language , spoken in parts of the northeastern United States and in Quebec, related to Western Abenaki .
A town in Hancock County , Maine , United States .
